title._content: Federal Building in Keene New Hampshire

description._content: TITLE Federal Building in Keene New Hampshire CREATOR Wardwell, Anne, Keene NH SUBJECT Post offices - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION "Perhaps the most successful modern building constructed on the street, the Federal Building is impressive for its design, size, and the excellent landscaping. Here is a monumental building which blends into the Main Street rows. The motif of the porch supports, although concrete, echos many of the wooden porches seen throughout the city."
